content: I already gave a 4 star review but it won't let me change it. I'm giving this app 3 stars mainly because: you cannot click on a member to see all of their posts [you only have a "feed"], and you do not get a notification when someone replies to your comment. In fact, you cannot even reply directly ... so all you can do is leave a comment and then later, scroll down through your feed to hopefully find that post you commented on [if you remember], and check if a response was given. :(
I love this app! It makes following THM coaches and finding different healthy things to eat so easy! Thanks Serene and Pearl!

It's a great *start*! I love the one time fee instead of monthly (I don't do monthly). I like keeping myself accountable and I love being inspired by others' yummy looking, on plan meals. The text box can be glitchy/ slow and I often want to say more than 180 charactersüòú It would be nice to see who is following me, be able to see who "liked" something, and be able to search for others based on their profile. I don't doubt it will improve with updates throughout the coming monthsüòä
I sure hope there's more to the app than this? It needs a recipe page! And maybe a meal plan suggestion page where mamas can share stuff!! Please add this! üôè

Such a fun app! A great way to stay on track with food and accountability. I love being connected with the thm community. My suggestion for improvement, it crashes when I try to take an in app photo. I can overcome that by taking a photo on my phone and uploading it, but it would be nice if that function worked. My other suggestion is notification. I don't know if someone commented on my post or who's following me.
I used for a few days and now I just get the splash screen and nothing. Hope it is fixed soon!

I'm liking the concept, but I'm having some glitches and I'm not sure how to try fixing. 1. About 8 times when I tried taking a photo of my food, the app would just shut down and I'd lose all the info I'd just typed in about that meal. I just purchased yesterday, so it happened a lot on one day. 2. When I tried to delete a misspelled word on the text box, instead of deleting it just kept typing the misspelled word over and over with more text rather than simply feeling that one word.
I really like this app. It's convenient having one place for my food journal & weight tracking. I think the price was a little high for what it is. I suggest adding a time stamp option also.
A great start!! Cant wait to see it get even better!!
Great so far! I know updates are coming to make it even better. Happy to have it for the new year

Journaling keeps me honest! When I allow others to see my journal, I am "inspired to be an inspiration to others," which helps me make wise choices. This app allows me to journal privately, OR publicly. A quick snap of a photo before I eat, and done. The developers ask for suggestions for improvement, so I expect this to become food-journaling perfection after a few updates in early 2021. *Expect some quirks with this first release.* And, a one-time payment instead of a subscription is nice!

This app would be so much better if it was combined with the THM Food Analyzer app. As a newbie I am constantly looking up what is an E vs S. If the two apps were combined I could enter what I ate and it would automatically tell me if it was an E, S, FP, etc.
It only shows the intro screen, can't get in to start a thing yet.
So amazing!
It's new and simple, excited to see the updates. Great tool if you follow thm lifestyle.

I love the concept, but it doesn't work that well. It gets stuck on a screen, and I have to shut it down. Sometimes my information will be there and sometimes it won't. I would like the ability to log other measurements sometime in the future as it is nice to see all the inches we lose.
Just got the app! Super excited to start using it ü§ó
I love this app!!
Love love love thm there recipes are amazing
Love the accountability and everything about this app. THM is where it's at!
It won't go beyond the welcome screen. Updated and restarted my phone and nothing. Had super high hopes and will revisit my review if and when I have a different experience. üòÄ
Love this app.
I can't get the "Find other Mamas" page to work. The little arrow just spins endlessly.
I love this app! This will be so helpful to keep me on track!
I love this app! There are all the tools needed to journal this healthy style and plan for success. I'm excited to dig in!
Love it!!
Yay! I am loving this first paid app from THM. Can't wait to see what fun things they are gonna do with this! This is a great tool for the THM journey.

I love the concepts and the positivity of this app! I think this app has features that I haven't seen before, like the selfie journal, the comparisons, and the panic button!! Plus, we get to see where the meals lie, S, E, FP, NOP. Loving this app so far!!
I had hoped it would give more information such as calories and nutrition of foods I am eating. I can easily track E or S meals.
A few kinks to work out, but I love it! I love being able to categorize my meals and log with a simple picture.

I downloaded this app as soon as I received my email. It has not worked it downloaded but has not moved of the sisters faces.I have waited over 24 hours to uninstalled, then reinstall to see if i could get it going. STILL NO LUCK! HELP!!!
Excited to connect with others and get more insight. It's a great App.

Didn't work at first, wouldn't even pull up a login screen, and none of the email login links would work. Super frustrating. I updated my phone to the latest OS, and boom, I'm in. So, try that if you are having the same problem.
It's easy to use

Love this app! Couldn't recommend it enough for newbies and for veterans like myself. I will say it was a little slow at the beginning but I know it's because of the overwhelming downloads. Give it a chance and it will rock your world! The panic button is the best. You get to hear sound bites from Serene and Pearl with ideas and encouragement it's just wonderful. Thank you so much for this!
Fantastic company. If it's not working right now it will soon. Great customer service!
Amazing!!!! Can't wait to make myself acountable!!! I love that I am the only one who can see my email and other stuff.

Love the smooth functionality and the one time price instead of a monthly membership fee. This app provides a great blend of community, goal-tracking, reminder setting and support. You can use it for community, support, and visual meal ideas as well as tracking progress visually and with weight and measurement statistics. It is not a calorie or fuel type tracker, in that it doesn't do the calculations for you, but you can track your meals, snacks, drinks, and what fuel types they are. My favorite feature so far has to be the panic button!
I'm so impressed! The Panic button is genius and the ability to log meals is so helpful! I'm genuinely impressed with the functionality! Love this!
The app won't open past the login screen. Once it is fixed and I can actually try the app I will update.
I am so looking forward to using this app. The heart and soul that was poured into it shows. I know it will quickly become a source of motivation and encouragement for me.
I'm so looking forward to this app. I know the heart and soul that was poured into this experience. I know it will become a source of motivation and encouragement for me.

So excited to use this. If its slow for you, give it a bit. They are working to get it smooth. I was able to open it up and use it a bit. Thankful for an APP for THM!!! The creators of this truly care about people, give them a chance to get it smooth if it's laggy.
I paid for the app and it will not go past the sign in. I sign in with email and it says already have and account, sign in with Google. Then doesn't give anyway to sign in. Very disappointed.
Wonderful company! Very useful app.
It will not let me sign in. Getting refundüò•
Stuck on the sign in screen.
I love this app and all that it does for my health!
I am so glad this app is out there! Great way to see foods I am eating and journal it too!

Love the concept of this app! Great resource of encouragement with the "panic" button! I am excited about the potential of this new app and the progress I hope to make in my weightloss and health-gaining journey this year. I am looking forward to having one place to keep my THM info, track meals, and keep up with other THMs without the extra distraction of fb.

App is not working. I get a screen that asks to sign in, but there are no fields to enter username and password, or buttons to click... just a blank screen that is titled "Welcome to the Journey: Please sign in or create a new account"
Woohoo!! Its here! Worth every cent.
So far...AMAZING
LOVE what it has/is so far! So happy it's finally available and I am looking forward to future features.
Very impressed with all you can do in this app. No glitches so far and I think the panic button is a fantastic idea and such a fun way to stay motivated .
Easy to use and wonderful to help track .easy and goals!
